試10次都失敗10次<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(成功左一次,入左區隊既...B隊,不過區隊本身就好細規模,所謂既B隊,只係去湊下人數,賺下你波衫錢,陪班A隊練波,幫佢地執頭執尾咁,完全唔會有比賽for我地,咁樣hea左一季之後就完左)<br />\n<br />\n到而家24歲,基本上已經放棄左呢個夢想,雖然要承認,要去接受一世都完成唔到呢個夢想係好sad<br />\n但至少叫做試過下,爭取過,都無悔lu<br />\n鬼叫自己無天份咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 特別係運動咁講求天份呢方面,練極都係好平庸,追唔到人地,係呢方面認命<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過都有KEEP住同朋友踢波,因為真心中意足球 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2316c91741fac072cfdf35f992b42d00de591135","tid":359614,"uid":86038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T17:43:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>足球員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可惜呢個夢想有年齡限制,自己無天份+太遲先想去追夢<br />\n人地一早7-8歲小朋友時呀爸呀媽已經帶佢地去開始參加乜隊乜隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細細個就成日踢草場,有正式既團隊,訓練,比賽等等,發現有天份就用心培養佢,大d就開始咩青年軍,預備隊,B隊,A隊大後備咁上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己就只係一路混混噩噩踢下街波,到18-19歲先覺醒想追下呢個夢,但已經無乜訓練咁大個既球隊<br />\n全部u16 u14 u12 u10 u8 咁落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唯有閒時自己練下,去報下區隊同見有乙丙組招募時試下<br />\n但一隊波選2x人,6-70人去選,好多都係本身已經踢開區隊/乙丙組/有長期草場比賽波底<br />\n自己呢,實力同經驗都欠奉,只係一心去試下,結果自然試10次都失敗10次<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(成功左一次,入左區隊既...B隊,不過區隊本身就好細規模,所謂既B隊,只係去湊下人數,賺下你波衫錢,陪班A隊練波,幫佢地執頭執尾咁,完全唔會有比賽for我地,咁樣hea左一季之後就完左)<br />\n<br />\n到而家24歲,基本上已經放棄左呢個夢想,雖然要承認,要去接受一世都完成唔到呢個夢想係好sad<br />\n但至少叫做試過下,爭取過,都無悔lu<br />\n鬼叫自己無天份咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 特別係運動咁講求天份呢方面,練極都係好平庸,追唔到人地,係呢方面認命<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過都有KEEP住同朋友踢波,因為真心中意足球 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認命 至少巴打你試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"276521bf722a7a386646a3fb82eff7e9a6f40da1","tid":359614,"uid":74380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T17:45:26.000Z","msg":"細個有學彈琴,做諗過做鋼琴家。果時參加左比賽,不過比賽前個半月有個好朋友發現有絕症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,果陣日日陪住希望佢唔好死,到比賽果日一心想令冠軍比佢睇等佢開心啲快啲好返,但結果緊係事與願違啦,拎唔到冠軍得季軍,過左半年多少少佢就過左身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,最後因為我覺得係我拎唔到冠軍所以佢先會死,所以就放棄左彈琴了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bce3217637037008d2a9c273bd47c532d8bc83d","tid":359614,"uid":48929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T17:47:03.000Z","msg":"拍拖"},{"pid":"b6facb44c8ec6199ceecd02b86bc3c11e7a7ff39","tid":359614,"uid":126590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T17:49:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個有學彈琴,做諗過做鋼琴家。果時參加左比賽,不過比賽前個半月有個好朋友發現有絕症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,果陣日日陪住希望佢唔好死,到比賽果日一心想令冠軍比佢睇等佢開心啲快啲好返,但結果緊係事與願違啦,拎唔到冠軍得季軍,過左半年多少少佢就過左身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,最後因為我覺得係我拎唔到冠軍所以佢先會死,所以就放棄左彈琴了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你呢個好可惜：(希望你有一日會彈返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a930d5d531fde79e3383831e6f01393baf8303c","tid":359614,"uid":136758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T17:51:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>細個想做空姐 <br />\n覺得空姐套制服好靚 又可以周圍飛<br />\n但越大個就覺得空姐同空中待應無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Same here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> In過fail令我放棄左"},{"pid":"6ab2249a431d8caad213d9e540579b31880587ef","tid":359614,"uid":74380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T18:16:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>細個有學彈琴,做諗過做鋼琴家。果時參加左比賽,不過比賽前個半月有個好朋友發現有絕症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,果陣日日陪住希望佢唔好死,到比賽果日一心想令冠軍比佢睇等佢開心啲快啲好返,但結果緊係事與願違啦,拎唔到冠軍得季軍,過左半年多少少佢就過左身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,最後因為我覺得係我拎唔到冠軍所以佢先會死,所以就放棄左彈琴了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你呢個好可惜：(希望你有一日會彈返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實鋼琴家呢樣野好似我呢啲柒頭皮點會做到丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 或者放棄可能對我黎講係一件好事既<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢件事都成十幾年前了,一向都好少同人提起,如果要我而家彈返應該同新手都冇乜分別,如果唔係有個契機令我彈返琴既話我諗我呢世都唔會再彈了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e27f080c6584f1454b242cba20952638e24edd2","tid":359614,"uid":86038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T06:52:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"229d184574e523fe0e65c53a05a86381b884c30e","tid":359614,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:02:35.000Z","msg":"想做大俠，維護世界和平，揚善懲惡。<br />\n<br />\n但當下只求每日返工無驚無險，盡時收工。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n儲夠錢然後十月辭工去半年旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07c9d674b74c4d69d95db729e2d1909afd35cdba","tid":359614,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:03:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想做大俠，維護世界和平，揚善懲惡。<br />\n<br />\n但當下只求每日返工無驚無險，*準*時收工。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n儲夠錢然後十月辭工去半年旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ae329769e06d91b749b0f2490d12b769ec6beca5","tid":359614,"uid":134781,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:04:32.000Z","msg":"私家偵探 <br />\n可惜 原來太靚仔 唔做得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3adbe5342bb535f07593b3ce038965be17c4bbe","tid":359614,"uid":111256,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:13:46.000Z","msg":"想做音樂監製<br />\n無天份<br />\n結果做左律師<br />\n<br />\n我都希望可以做番音樂既"},{"pid":"b130e5bada6bfe140e3501a386b7d1aeedcf3184","tid":359614,"uid":86038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T13:18:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想做音樂監製<br />\n無天份<br />\n結果做左律師<br />\n<br />\n我都希望可以做番音樂既</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9b9b3dadce9aa93b3fd14565c2b4e96eb38ab60","tid":359614,"uid":133435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T13:47:24.000Z","msg":"曾經希望可以全心全意做木製品，做手工，畫畫，咁就可以隨時整野俾自己愛既人，二來可以建立個人品牌，賺個錢生活... 但夢想終歸只係夢想<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e32a334b1c581e9b3e0b6ecab66415a4c3a96e97","tid":359614,"uid":2386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T13:51:19.000Z","msg":"做飛機師<br />\n當知道自己好深近視同散光之後就放棄咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac08efb780b2d6aa4387197a42bac709d22de9b9","tid":359614,"uid":53254,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T13:53:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想做音樂監製<br />\n無天份<br />\n結果做左律師<br />\n<br />\n我都希望可以做番音樂既</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講到退而求其次. 點知係律師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"284a566f7056476c57062ef5aa8034581dafafa3","tid":359614,"uid":105130,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T14:00:11.000Z","msg":"一個人行太平洋屋脊步道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過放棄咗"},{"pid":"a5eb254b1fdc90d30e37dcd0fe544f4a02e43223","tid":359614,"uid":86038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T14:09:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想做音樂監製<br />\n無天份<br />\n結果做左律師<br />\n<br />\n我都希望可以做番音樂既</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講到退而求其次. 點知係律師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁如果條路唔係佢鍾意既 律唔律師都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a0e732af0cc6c475f6475abc9cd4f27304ef73","tid":359614,"uid":132738,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T14:30:13.000Z","msg":"細個冇乜夢想 唯一想嘅就係可以成立一個安穩嘅家庭 好似細個咁<br />\n冇乜大志 淨係想好似老豆咁 有個老婆 有班豬朋狗友肯同自己分擔下壓力就夠<br />\n到而家 老豆老母離左婚 一個朋友又冇 啲女仔見我咁撚頹又唔想理我<br />\n而家都冇乜動力再去建立關係<br />\n唉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bee5a67d7830d8ac56eb6d930153542b8a35282","tid":359614,"uid":79971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T15:23:52.000Z","msg":"點解無人讙月想灌籃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好想試下但係自己又唔高又好難練到<br />\n有試過練但係感覺好遙不可及<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0433efc6f1efcb94fe12e133ab574a5764e35e97","tid":359614,"uid":88182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T15:42:47.000Z","msg":"曾經我有一班志同道合既手足同我夾band 果陣我真係諗住夾到老 ，果陣有個夢想就係可以出我地屬於我地既歌，然後會上toutube之類既地方有過10萬既點擊 有人賞識我地，可以參加比賽 接d job番黎賺少少錢，開開心心咁玩落去，可惜到最尾工作原因拆散我地。 <br />\n我真係有d唔甘心。點解要生係香港 每日做到on99無哂人生理想 連少少既夢想既希望都無"},{"pid":"632de587b79e12a63985fe0679d6037267c7b7b7","tid":359614,"uid":49353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T15:55:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>曾經我有一班志同道合既手足同我夾band 果陣我真係諗住夾到老 ，果陣有個夢想就係可以出我地屬於我地既歌，然後會上toutube之類既地方有過10萬既點擊 有人賞識我地，可以參加比賽 接d job番黎賺少少錢，開開心心咁玩落去，可惜到最尾工作原因拆散我地。 <br />\n我真係有d唔甘心。點解要生係香港 每日做到on99無哂人生理想 連少少既夢想既希望都無</blockquote><br />\n巴打你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細個好想做DJ 因爲覺得佢哋可以成日播歌之餘又可以分享所見所聞，好似好好玩咁<br />\n直至有一年暑假小DJ訓練計劃，一向唔係好講嘢嘅我，為咗參加到，做咗好多準備功夫，練好表達能力，交完表之後每一日都好期待有offer㗎，但最後梗係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後到大學嗰時發覺都要返咁上下學歷先入到行，自比不如，所以就放棄了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca563ef04fcd94c8c65283e0403f21a7a511cfb","tid":359614,"uid":66759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T15:59:14.000Z","msg":"以前細個只係想搵份普通的工作 工作量普通<br />\n然後自己一個人生活 假期自己一個休息 偶然約朋友<br />\n自己一間屋 有時候出下國 有時候放下長假<br />\n<br />\n而家份工應該係最辛苦嗰5%西工 工餘又要進修 人工又唔係多<br />\n之後又要供養老婆仔女 無曬私人時間金錢 無幾個知心朋友<br />\n屋企已經唔係自己一個 無錢出國 公司極難放假<br />\n<br />\n根本就係行屍走肉 日日勁早起身勁夜收工 燃燒生命到死"},{"pid":"c46bc012981739ccee6ff5b98691b749114f655c","tid":359614,"uid":86530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:04:46.000Z","msg":"曾經講過中七前要入到樽<br />\n<br />\n結果係三十都嚟緊都未掂到框"},{"pid":"78e940630fae25ddab931350b64ed23753a3494d","tid":359614,"uid":58920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:13:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f38299acb37d11b90fe8090bf9376f30c94c4b7b","tid":359614,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:17:18.000Z","msg":"行入堆填區"},{"pid":"748f8f57298d1e448ba69e4d64c9b3becf49b737","tid":359614,"uid":66286,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:40:51.000Z","msg":"做歌手<br />\n<br />\n細個已經好中意唱歌跳舞<br />\n但係又唔太敢 <br />\n媽媽問我join 唔join d班又唔敢報<br />\n到大個<br />\n唱歌都淨係敢係k房唱or自己屋企<br />\n冇參加比賽<br />\n到依家有依個勇氣啦<br />\n但已經大個歌冇機會<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a94869aff9333f345ca128a37583dfc91aadc622","tid":359614,"uid":124560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:42:49.000Z","msg":"夢想係宇宙探險家，以前會畫好多火箭，睇好多太空探索嘅書，細個已經知道有voyager1,2 兩架無人太空船，仲會收集一種印有唔同衛星嘅襟章，同睇有關天文嘅書<br />\n<br />\n上左中學我咩興趣都無哂，連做人都提唔起勁，日日被逼温書，做練習，再補習，對學習再無興趣<br />\n<br />\n所幸係自己最近有新興趣，遺憾係細個心願未了，只能為過去哭訴"},{"pid":"7b6c90118a7f9b9a52a81e10e0c19a29fdec922e","tid":359614,"uid":37942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:53:40.000Z","msg":"溝哂啲靚女<br />\n<br />\n但自己零口才，一個都溝唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed480a78c99eaf3bb778bfccffbc8eaa6e8fa313","tid":359614,"uid":76091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:55:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做飛機師<br />\n當知道自己好深近視同散光之後就放棄咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我讀中學時都曾經ff過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我英文唔掂+講嘢1999+數學差+矮(雖然呢樣唔太關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)+個人唔得淡定好易騰雞(呢樣先係死症)<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc3f009540c345b4c1d2cc0d5a06cabd5b43073c","tid":359614,"uid":37942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:56:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做飛機師<br />\n當知道自己好深近視同散光之後就放棄咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我讀中學時都曾經ff過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我英文唔掂+講嘢1999+數學差+矮(雖然呢樣唔太關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)+個人唔得淡定好易騰雞(呢樣先係死症)<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你有咩掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6de10e2dcbbf0d538ebb57f935eec8965a8a02d","tid":359614,"uid":135293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:58:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做飛機師<br />\n當知道自己好深近視同散光之後就放棄咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係唔夠高<br />\n15X 絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d91f7e1742f5588e8f6cc02c9555faab64f8519c","tid":359614,"uid":45102,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:59:02.000Z","msg":"參加奧運<br />\n曾經入過港青 不過每次比賽都會揀人(個人項目運動)<br />\n所以每次報完名都揀唔到我<br />\n我一直無放棄<br />\n一路keep住每個星期去練足3日港青<br />\n入隊一年冇離開過中國以外既國家比賽<br />\n開始心灰意冷<br />\n點解每次都係出個幾個人<br />\n成隊港青二三十人<br />\n其他人只係幫佢地練習既棋子<br />\n所以退隊了<br />\n同時亦都放棄左個樣運動<br />\n直到宜家冇再玩過"},{"pid":"e42e0906622111b21894a9c80cea16591fcf2d90","tid":359614,"uid":124560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:02:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>參加奧運<br />\n曾經入過港青 不過每次比賽都會揀人(個人項目運動)<br />\n所以每次報完名都揀唔到我<br />\n我一直無放棄<br />\n一路keep住每個星期去練足3日港青<br />\n入隊一年冇離開過中國以外既國家比賽<br />\n開始心灰意冷<br />\n點解每次都係出個幾個人<br />\n成隊港青二三十人<br />\n其他人只係幫佢地練習既棋子<br />\n所以退隊了<br />\n同時亦都放棄左個樣運動<br />\n直到宜家冇再玩過</blockquote><br />\n巴打有無為理想付出過淚水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咩項目，介唔介意講"},{"pid":"66a171b724d754f726a3c4c8a3f5d6a41584858d","tid":359614,"uid":76091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:04:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做飛機師<br />\n當知道自己好深近視同散光之後就放棄咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我讀中學時都曾經ff過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我英文唔掂+講嘢1999+數學差+矮(雖然呢樣唔太關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)+個人唔得淡定好易騰雞(呢樣先係死症)<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你有咩掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" clas