ke":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:18:06.000Z","msg":"做農夫，種大麻俾有需要的人，但這裡是香港，一個不能實現的夢想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"babf7787df0e9bbb7768ff835c8502e8415c1277","tid":359614,"uid":43569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T18:00:34.000Z","msg":"想做一個好大隻時嘅人<br />\n想保護身邊想保護嘅人<br />\n可惜操左差唔多兩年<br />\n有一次last set想做重d<br />\n唔小心整傷左個背<br />\n睇左好多跌打中醫西醫都睇唔好<br />\n到而家差唔多傷左一年<br />\n都仲未好返哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔想放棄 但個天好似唔係好支持我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b81757c72bb9d64c0b45efb925b540ac36d1e6a","tid":359614,"uid":43569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T18:01:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想做一個好大隻<del>時</del>嘅人<br />\n想保護身邊想保護嘅人<br />\n可惜操左差唔多兩年<br />\n有一次last set想做重d<br />\n唔小心整傷左個背<br />\n睇左好多跌打中醫西醫都睇唔好<br />\n到而家差唔多傷左一年<br />\n都仲未好返哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔想放棄 但個天好似唔係好支持我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e299f659f1e9c7810f4bc1f8340032c10b1c970a","tid":359614,"uid":111256,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T18:14:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想做音樂監製<br />\n無天份<br />\n結果做左律師<br />\n<br />\n我都希望可以做番音樂既</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講到退而求其次. 點知係律師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁如果條路唔係佢鍾意既 律唔律師都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n各行各業都係咁架啦<br />\n我啲同事都係想做 足球員 結他手 科學家 果啲<br />\n邊有人我的志願係做律師<br />\n<br />\n去到最後 做唔到我的志願 咪轉做其他野囉"},{"pid":"a933be2f5ade1e15948fe141adbf357310be6bf5","tid":359614,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":